NOT SEEKING, just throwing in a joke because i&#x27;m feeling so: One day a man goes to a pet shop to buy a parrot. The assistant takes the man to the parrot section and asks the man to choose one. The man asks, &#x27;&#x27;How much is the yellow one?&#x27;&#x27;
The assistant says, &#x27;&#x27;$2000.&#x27;&#x27; The man is shocked and asks the assistant why it&#x27;s so expensive. The assistant explains, &#x27;&#x27;This parrot is a very special one. He knows typewriting and can type really fast.&#x27;&#x27;
&#x27;&#x27;What about the green one?&#x27;&#x27; the man asks.
The assistant says, &#x27;&#x27;He costs $5000 because he knows typewriting and can answer incoming telephone calls and takes notes.&#x27;&#x27;
&#x27;&#x27;What about the red one?&#x27;&#x27; the man asks.
The assistant says, &#x27;&#x27;That one&#x27;s $10,000.&#x27;&#x27;
The man says, &#x27;&#x27;What does HE do?&#x27;&#x27;
The assistant says, &#x27;&#x27;I don&#x27;t know, but the other two call him boss.&#x27;&#x27;
